metadata.name: basta
metadata.description:
This photo was taken in 2013 in Basta, the historical district of Beirut, one of the most beautiful cities in the world.

As an artist I would like to start my minting with these unique photo. This photo, taken in an environment where people are uncomfortable to even see someone with a camera, were digitally edited and achieved the highest possible resolution.

-2448 × 3264 - 94 dpi / 26x34 inch - 66x86 cm max.-

This photo is unique and has archival value besides its artistic value.
